description: The objective of fund is to replicate, as closely as possible, the performance of the FTSE MTS Eurozone Government Broad IG 7-10Y Index (the Index), whether the Index rises or falls. The target for maximum tracking err between changes in the Funds NAV and that of the Index is 2%.
name: Amundi ETF Govt Bond Euro Broad Investment Grade 7-10 UCITS ETF DR
